labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - Approved Re-Audit (90 Days)
labels.value: Approved to produce on the condition that all red flagged audit findings are closed or downgraded to yellow within 90 days of the re-audit date of {!FormatedAuditDt} . If the red flags are not closed after 90 days, all production must stop until they are addressed.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - Conditional Approval Expired
labels.value: Not eligible to apply for a waiver review and must be re-audited by NBCU and re-approved before production is allowed. Please ensure that the factory completes and returns the NBCU Audit Application.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - Conditionally Approved
labels.value: Approved to produce on the condition that all yellow flagged audit findings are corrected by {!FormatAprovalExpirtationDate} , and regular progress updates are provided to our auditors.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - Conditionally Approved (Pending Rejection)
labels.value: Factory is facing rejection and must provide evidence of correction and a progress update to our auditors this week.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - Correction Required
labels.value: An NBCU audit has been conducted and the factory must close or downgrade all open red flagged findings before we can conditionally approve the factory. No production is allowed until the red flag findings have been closed and an approval letter is received.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - Lapsed - Re-Audit Required
labels.value: It has been over one year since the NBCU audit was conducted and approval was not obtained. The audit is expired and an NBCU re-audit is required. Factory is not eligible to apply for a waiver review.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - Official Approval - Expired
labels.value: The NBCU audit has expired and the factory is required to re-obtain approval before production is allowed. Please apply for a waiver review or NBCU re-audit.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - Officially Approved
labels.value: Approved to produce until {!FormatAprovalExpirtationDate}, when a waiver review or NBCU re-audit is required to obtain re-approval.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - On Hold
labels.value: The factory had accepted the NBCU audit but the audit was placed on hold due to {!HoldReason} .

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - Pending Rejection
labels.value: Factory is pending rejection. Please push the factory to provide evidence of correction for the open audit findings or source from another factory that is willing to cooperate.

This factory was audited by NBCU and rejected due to {!RejectionReason}. If you would like to use this factory, an NBCU re-audit is required and all red flagged audit findings must be either closed or downgraded in order to obtain at least conditional approval. In to proceed with an NBCU re-audit, 100% committment is required from the factory to closing out all audit findings. Please inform us if you would like to proceed with an NBCU re-audit.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - Rejected Child Labor

labels.value: Not eligible to apply for a waiver review and must be audited by NBCU and approved before production is allowed. Please ensure that the factory completes and returns the NBCU Audit Application.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-NBCU Audit - Under Scheduling
labels.value: The factory has accepted the NBCU audit and our auditors are working to schedule an audit date with the factory.
An audit will not be requested at this time as long as all production/branding is done in {!Factorycountry}.
Not eligible to apply for a waiver review and must be audited by NBCU and approved before production is allowed. Please ensure that the factory completes and returns the NBCU Audit Application.
Production is not authorized in this country.
Approved to produce until {!FormatAprovalExpirtationDate}, when re-approval is required. Factory is subject to an NBCU spot check audit.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-Waiver Review - Approved (Spot Check Passed)
labels.value: Approved to produce until {!FormatAprovalExpirtationDate}, when a re-approval is required.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-Waiver Review - Approved (Spot Check Required)
labels.value: Approved to produce until {!FormatAprovalExpirtationDate}, when re-approval is required. Factory is required to undergo an NBCU spot check audit.
Waiver was disapproved and the factory is required to undergo an NBCU audit. Please ensure that the factory completes and returns the NBCU Audit Application.
The waiver approval has expired and the factory is required to obtain approval before production is allowed. Please apply for a waiver review or NBCU audit.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-Waiver Review - Pending Documentation
labels.value: Pending documentation. A waiver application, current audit report (within 10 months), and evidence of correction is required in order to apply for a waiver review.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-Waiver Review - Pending Review
labels.value: Pending review of documents. Documentation was received and is under review. Please allow two weeks for processing.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-Waiver Review - Spot Check Failed
labels.value: Factory has failed the NBCU spot check and all production must stop.

labels.shortDescription: GBS Status Note-Waiver Review or NBCU Audit Required
labels.value: Factory must be approved by NBCUniversal Global Brand Standards team before production is allowed, either by a waiver review or NBCU audit. Pending applicable documentation.
If submitting a Subcontracted Factory,input the Primary Factory.
